'''* White Paper: Blockchain for Scaling Climate Action.  Crypto Sustainability Coalition’s Working Group on Web3 Climate Action, WEF, April 2023'''

URL = https://www.weforum.org/publications/blockchain-for-scaling-climate-action/

''"The environment and climate sectors require digital transformation to keep up with the changing planetary ecosystem and to coordinate urgent and global action in areas including biodiversity loss, disaster displacement and energy grid deficiencies."''


=Description=

"exploring the relationship between blockchain innovation and climate action, focusing on real work examples and use cases. It is intended as a primer for those unfamiliar with regenerative finance (ReFi) and a guide to those incorporating blockchain technologies into decarbonization or net-zero commitments. Investigating how blockchain can incentivize a planet-positive economy focused on financing regeneration and climate action at scale, the paper calls for thoughtful coordination, meaningful action, education and regulation to accelerate the adoption and implementation of blockchain across decarbonization sectors."

